^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Basically there are 3 rules you can use to determine if you  have a 2 club opener.|
PG| ***** 121 ***** |


AT|
First, is if you have a balanced hand with 22 or more|
PG| ***** 122 ***** |


AT|
Second, is if you have a major then you can use Marty Bergen's 4 and 4 rule. If you have 4 quick tricks and no more than 4 losers, but real losers, not losing trick count losers, you can open 2C.|
PG| ***** 123 ***** |


